---
import LandingSegmentLayout from "../layouts/LandingSegmentLayout.astro";
import ProcessPhase from "./ProcessPhase";
---

<LandingSegmentLayout>
  <div class="py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span
        class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm font-mono tracking-wider mb-6"
      >
        OUR METHODOLOGY
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        From Vision to<br />
        <span class="gradient-text">Production Intelligence</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
        We don't just build systems—we architect custom analytics tools that
        evolve with your organization. Our methodology ensures rapid iteration,
        continuous improvement, and measurable business impact.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Phase 1 -->
        <ProcessPhase
          client:load
          number="01"
          title="Discovery & Architecture"
          description="We start by understanding your data landscape, business objectives, and technical constraints. Through workshops, data audits, and stakeholder interviews, we map your current state and design the target unified architecture."
          items={[
            "Data source inventory & assessment",
            "Stakeholder requirement gathering",
            "Technical architecture design",
            "Proof-of-concept development",
            "Risk assessment & mitigation planning",
          ]}
        />

        <!-- Phase 2 -->
        <ProcessPhase
          client:load
          number="02"
          title="Data Integration & Pipeline Development"
          description="We build the foundational data layer, connecting all your sources into a unified pipeline. This includes ETL/ELT processes, data quality checks, schema evolution, and real-time streaming capabilities."
          items={[
            "Data pipeline architecture & implementation",
            "Schema design & normalization",
            "Data quality monitoring & validation",
            "Real-time streaming infrastructure",
            "Data lineage & documentation",
          ]}
        />

        <!-- Phase 3 -->
        <ProcessPhase
          client:load
          number="03"
          title="Spatial-Temporal Model Development"
          description="We develop custom spatial and time series models tailored to your specific use cases. This includes temporal feature engineering, spatial data preparation, forecasting model training, validation, and deployment into production inference pipelines."
          items={[
            "Time series feature engineering & preparation",
            "Spatial pattern analysis & clustering",
            "Forecasting model training & validation",
            "Geographic intelligence model development",
            "A/B testing frameworks for temporal models",
          ]}
        />

        <!-- Phase 4 -->
        <ProcessPhase
          client:load
          number="04"
          title="Application & Interface Development"
          description="We build the interfaces that make your analytics tools accessible—custom dashboards, APIs, visualization tools, and natural language query interfaces that enable decision-makers to interact with the system."
          items={[
            "User experience design & prototyping",
            "Dashboard & visualization development",
            "API design & implementation",
            "Natural language query interfaces",
            "Mobile & responsive design",
          ]}
        />

        <!-- Phase 5 -->
        <ProcessPhase
          client:load
          number="05"
          title="Deployment & Production Operations"
          description="We deploy your system to production with full observability, monitoring, and automated scaling. This includes CI/CD pipelines, infrastructure as code, security hardening, and operational runbooks."
          items={[
            "Infrastructure provisioning & configuration",
            "CI/CD pipeline setup",
            "Monitoring & alerting systems",
            "Security hardening & compliance",
            "Documentation & training",
          ]}
        />

        <!-- Phase 6 -->
        <ProcessPhase
          client:load
          number="06"
          title="Continuous Improvement & Evolution"
          description="Analytics tools are living systems. We establish feedback loops, model retraining pipelines, and continuous monitoring to ensure your system improves over time and adapts to changing conditions."
          items={[
            "Performance monitoring & optimization",
            "Model retraining & updates",
            "Feature expansion & enhancement",
            "User feedback integration",
            "Strategic roadmap planning",
          ]}
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 bg-gray-900 text-white p-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
          Agile, Iterative, Results-Driven
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
          We don't wait until the end to show value. Our methodology delivers
          working data capabilities in weeks, not months. Each phase builds on
          the previous one, ensuring continuous progress and early validation of
          assumptions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LandingSegmentLayout>
